name: CryptoBaby
description: CryptoBaby’s is a free to mint NFT collection where the goal is to educate people on Crtyptocurrency and NFT’s. Many people are interested in Crtypo and NFT’s, but don’t have the knowledge to participate safely. This NFT community will foster education of Crtypto and NFT’s through fun! There will be an arc built with utility for members. The community will drive the project.
